quran[11{c,v,t}:
39,57,Aw taqoola law annal laaha hadaanee lakuntu minal muttaqeen
39,58,Aw taqoola heena taral 'azaaba law anna lee karratan fa akoona minal muhsineen
39,59,Balaa qad jaaa'atka Asyaatee fakazzabta bihaa wastak barta wa kunta minal kaafireen
39,60,Wa Yawmal Qiyaamati taral lazeena kazaboo 'alallaahi wujoohuhum muswaddah; alaisa fee Hahannama maswal lilmutakabbireen
39,61,Wa yunajjil laahul lazee nat taqaw bimafaazatihim laa yamassuhumus sooo'u wa laa hum uahzanoon
39,62,Allaahu khaaliqu kulli shai'inw wa Huwa 'alaa kulli shai'inw Wakeel
39,63,Lahoo maqaaleedus sa maawaati wal ard; wallazeena kafaroo bi ayaatil laahi ulaaa'ika humul khaasiroon (section 6)
39,64,Qul afaghairal laahi taamurooonneee a'budu ayyuhal jaahiloon
39,65,Wa laqad oohiya ilaika wa ilal lazeena min qablika la in ashrakta la yahbatanna 'amalu ka wa latakoonanna minal khaasireen
39,66,Balil laahha fa'bud wa kum minash shaakireen
39,67,Wa maa qadarul laaha haqqa qadrihee wal ardu jamee 'an qabdatuhoo Yawmal Qiyaamit wassamaawaatu matwiyyaatum biyameenih; Subhaanahoo wa Ta'aalaa 'amma yushrikoon
